        {
            "title": "恒大案開庭｜恒大集資欺詐案深圳開審 許家印當庭認罪 法院將擇期宣判",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4PSme4rXbwATomKb4ehK9Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/696012129099035bd1e4c1142d3b3b78\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據官媒《新華社》報道，恒大欺詐案昨日（13日）起在深圳開審，作為恒大創辦人的被告<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"許家印\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:許家印;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/許家印\">許家印</a>當庭表示認罪，承認包括集資詐騙和單位行賄的多項指控，法庭將擇期宣判；他在約三年前因涉嫌犯罪被採取強制措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報道指，廣東省深圳市中級人民法院在周一及周二（13及14日）就深圳市人民檢察院提起的公訴進行公開開庭審理，被告單位包括恒大集團及恒大地產集團有限公司，許家印則以個人身份受審。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其中恒大集團被控非法吸收公眾存款、集資詐騙、違法發放貸款、欺詐發行證券、違規披露重要信息、單位行賄；恒大地產集團有限公司被控欺詐發行證券。許家印個人除了上述多項罪名，還額外被控非法運用資金及職務侵佔。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fd8ed36f-509f-3717-b190-4d3a599714d4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">庭審中，法庭主持控辯雙方圍繞指控的事實進行了法庭調查及法庭辯論，被告單位、許家印進行了最後陳述。許家印當庭表示認罪悔罪，法庭將擇期宣判。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報部份人大代表、政協委員、被告人親屬及集資參與人代表等亦有出席旁聽。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E6%A1%88%E9%96%8B%E5%BA%AD-%E6%81%92%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87%E6%AC%BA%E8%A9%90%E6%A1%88%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%96%8B%E5%AF%A9-%E8%A8%B1%E5%AE%B6%E5%8D%B0%E7%95%B6%E5%BA%AD%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA-%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%B0%87%E6%93%87%E6%9C%9F%E5%AE%A3%E5%88%A4-080000900.html",
